\section*{Preoperative Fasting for Adults to Prevent Peri-operative Complications. A Cochrane Review (Brady et al., 2003)}

This review was undertaken to systematically review the effect of different on preoperative fasting regimes on perioperative complications and patient wellbeing in different adult populations. Randomised controlled trials which compared the effect on post-operative complications of different fasting regimes on adults were selected.

